::Bloodystrike::

Bloodystrike raises an eyebrow, looking at Snitch. "I'm 
Bloodystrike," he says for the third time that day, "Are you the 
merchants?"

> ::Snitch::
> 
> He suppresses the urge to laugh as he grabs hold of the vine with 
his feet
> and leaps down the side of the tree, using the vine like a bungee, 
rushing
> in front of Bloodystrike's face! "Hello! I Snitch!" The small 
orange monkey
> burst out into laughter.
